name: Plastic Packaging, Tea Bags
description:
3D model gif, 10/10 ed. Based on PLASTIC AND VIRTUAL PACKAGING: an immersive artwork available in VR.

Mountains of plastic and 3D-generated packaging interrogate our (dis-)connection with reality.

Tea is not only sold in individual bags, these bags are protected in individual plastic bags, themselves sold in boxes that are transported in other boxes. 

More info: https://bruchansky.name/2022/01/18/plastic-and-virtual-packaging/
